name: Kessel Run
Lore: 'Planet Kessel has infamous glitterstim spice mines attracting smugglers and pirates. A ''Kessel run'' is a long, dangerous hyper-route they must travel quickly.',
Text: 'Deploy on Kessel. Target one of your smugglers at another system. X=parsec distance between the two systems. When target reaches Kessel, opponent draws destiny. If = 0, starship lost. Otherwise, by returning to first system, ''retrieve'' X Lost Force.',
